  "body": "We should show the stack trace that we have when there's an OOG error.\r\n\r\nI created a branch with a WIP commit that shows how this could be done: https://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/tree/oog-stack-traces\r\n\r\nThe commit is: b62502c09c5b55d0f17268f55f2be7fa979fad8c\r\n\r\nI re-used the `CUSTOM_ERROR` frame to simplify things, but we should use a new type of frame for this. Also, we should check that the last frame is indeed of that type here:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/blob/b62502c09c5b55d0f17268f55f2be7fa979fad8c/packages/hardhat-core/src/internal/hardhat-network/provider/node.ts#L1208",
